1480: /*
1481:  * Every module resolution kind can has its specific understanding how to load module from a specific path on disk
1482:  * I.e. for path '/a/b/c':
1483:  * - Node loader will first to try to check if '/a/b/c' points to a file with some supported extension and if this fails
